data.description: Welcome home to 6998 Augusta Dr! Sellers are offering a $3k credit for a rate buydown! Info in photos. This stunning 3 bedroom, 3 bath residence with a 3 car garage offers a perfect blend of style and functionality. The main floor features LVP flooring, providing both durability and beauty. The primary bedroom, located on the main floor, boasts a bathroom with double vanity sinks and a spacious walk-in closet. The kitchen offers 42” cabinets that are soft-close, a farmhouse sink, under cabinet lighting, 7ft island, and stunning granite countertops that make cooking a breeze. Pet owners will love the thoughtful addition of a pet shower in the laundry room, ensuring your furry friends are always pampered. The finished basement with egress adds even more space for recreation or relaxation. Solar panels in the house save you money and energy- an added bonus! Step outside to your fenced-in backyard, a private oasis for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day.
